      "Price locking behavior — whether the price at cart-add, checkout-initiation, or payment-confirmation is the binding price",
      "Whether partial inventory fulfillment is allowed (customer wants 5, only 3 available)",
      "Refund amount calculation when discounts were applied — refund at paid price or list price",
      "Whether reservation timeout is a hard 15 minutes or resets on customer activity"
    ],
    "assumptions": [
      "The 15-minute timeout is a hard wall clock limit from checkout initiation, not reset by activity",
      "The 30-day refund window is inclusive (day 30 is the last eligible day)",
      "Discount exclusivity applies at the order level, not the line-item level, based on the phrase 'per order'",
